data.description: REDUCED AGAIN! Come see this remodeled 3 BR, 2 BA bi-Level home located near Otero Jr. College & Tippy Martinez Park. The home features all new flooring and fresh paint throughout, a large lower level family room and lower level master bedroom with its own bathroom and walk-in closet. In addition there is a 1-car attached garage with new door, an additional detached 2-car garage with plenty of storage space, a 2-tier deck in the fenced backyard perfect for entertaining, and a newer roof. SELLER IS NOW OFFERING $5000 TO BUYER AT CLOSING AND WANTS OFFERS!
